race.comment: JIMARY BOB (2) continues to race in super honest form hitting the frame at all three career runs, winning two back before finishing third last time (19.86) over 366m at Capalaba. Goes well from this draw. Rates highly here and will go close. BLUE LAKODA (3) is looking to continue her winning ways off a decent 16.59 success in a Maiden at this track. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. MINTER THRILL (4) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when second (19.68) in a Grade 6 at this track. Key player on best and worth another try. ALES AND NAILS (6) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.
